   I'm a Software Engineer who is passionate about constructing servers and specializing in crafting robust and scalable backend solutions. My focus as a software engineer extends beyond code – it's about creating technology that elevates individuals and contributes to the building of thriving communities. Some technologies I enojy working with include Reactjs, Nodejs, and GraphQL.
